hadiths[25]{hadithnumber,text}:
2483,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( rajab 7 hijri mein) saahil bahar ki taraf aik lashkar bheja aur iska ameer abu-Ubaida bin-Jarraah (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya. faujiyon ki tadaad teen so thi aur main bhi unmein Sharik tha. ham nikley aur abhi rastey hi mein they ke khane-pine ka saman khatm ho gaya. abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne hukm diya ke tamam fauji apne toshey (jo kuchh bhi baqi reh gaey hon) aik jagah jama kar dein. sab kuchh jama karne ke baad khajooron ke kal 2 thailey ho sakey aur rozaana hamein usi mein se thodi thodi khajoor khaney ke liye milney lagi jab iska bhi aksar hissey khatm ho gaya to hamein sirf eik-eik khajoor miltii rahi. main (wahab-bin-Kaisaan) ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha bhala aik khajoor se kya hota hoga? unhon-ne batlaya ke uski qadr hamein us waqt malum hui jab wo bhi khatm ho gaee thi. unhon-ne bayan kya ke aakhir ham samandar tak pahunch gaey. ittifaq se samandar mein hamein aik aisi machhli mil gaee jo (apne jism mein) pahaad ki tarah malum hoti thi. Sara lashkar us machhli ko atthaara raaton tak khata raha. phir abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski donon pasliyon ko khada karne ka hukm diya. uske baad oonton ko unke taley se chalney ka hukm diya aur wo un pasliyon ke nichey se ho kar guzrey, lekin oont ne unko chhuwa tak nahi."
2484,"( jange-Hawaazin mein) logon ke toshey khatm ho gaey aur faqr w mohtaajii aa gaee, to log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. apne oonton ko zabah karne ki ijazat leney (taake unhiin ke gosht se pet bhar sakein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ijazat de di. rastey mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki mulaqat unse ho gaee to unhein bhi un logon ne itlaa di. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha oonton ko kaat daalogey to phir tum kaisey zinda rahogey. chunanche aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha, ya Rasulullah! agar unhon-ne oont bhi zabah kar liye to phir ye log kaisey zinda rahengey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha, tamam logon mein elaan kar do ke unke paas jo kuchh toshey bach rahe hain wo lekar yahan aa jaaein. uske liye aik chamdey ka dastar-khuwaan bichhaa diya gaya aur logon ne toshey usi dastar-khuwaan par la kar rakh diye. uske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey aur is mein barkat ki dua farmai. ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir sab logon ko apne apney bartanon ke sath bulaya aur sab ne donon hathon se toshey apne bartanon mein bhar liye. jab sab log bhar chukey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur ye ke main Allah ka sachcha rasool hoon.''"
2485,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Asr ki Namaz padh kar oont zabah kartey to unhein das hisson mein taqseem kartey aur phir suraj ghurub honey se pahley hi ham iska pakka hua gosht bhi kha letey.
2486,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, qabila ash'ar ke logon ka jab jihad ke mauqe par khane-pine ka saman kam ho jata ya Madina (ke qiyaam) mein unke baal bachchon ke liye khaney ki kami ho jati to jo kuchh bhi unke paas khane-pine ka saman hota to wo aik kapdey mein jama kar letey hain. phir aapas mein aik bartan se barabar taqseem kar letey hain. to wo mere hain aur main unka hun."
2487,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke liye farz zakat ka bayan tahreer kya tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muqarrar ki thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab kisi maal mein 2 aadmi saajhii hon to wo zakat mein aik doosrey se barabar barabar mujraa kar lein (yani zakat ki raqam aapas mein barabar taqseem kar lein).
2488,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maqam zul-Hulaifa mein thahrey huey they. logon ko bhook lagi idhar ( ghaneemat mein) oont aur bakriyan mili thin. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lashkar ke peechhey ke logon mein they. logon ne jaldi ki aur) taqseem se pahley hi ( zabah karke haandiyaan chadhaa din. lekin baad main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur wo haandiyaan aundha di gaiin. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko taqseem kya aur das bakriyon ko aik oont ke barabar rakha. aik oont usmein se bhag gaya to log usey pakadney ki koshish karne lagey. lekin us ne sab ko thakaa diya. qaum ke paas ghodey kam they. aik sahabi teer lekar oont ki taraf jhaptey. Allah ne usko thehra diya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke in janwaron mein bhi janglii janwaron ki tarah sarkashi hoti hai. isliye in janwaron mein se bhi agar koi tumhen aajiz kar de to iske sath tum aisa hi mamla kya karo. phir mere dada ne arz kya ke kal dushman ke hamle ka khof hai, hamarey paas chhuriyaan nahi hain (talwaaron se zabah karein to unke kharaab honey ka dar hai jabke jang samney hai) kya ham baans ke khapchii se zabah kar saktey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jo cheez bhi khoon baha de aur zabiha par Allah Taala ka naam liya gaya ho, to iske khaney mein koi harj nahi. siwaey daant aur naakhun ke. uski wjah main tumhen bataataa hun. daant to haddi hai aur naakhun habshiyon ki chhuri hai."
2489,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya tha ke koi shakhs apne sathiyon ki ijazat ke baghair (dastar-khaan par) 2-2 khajoor aik sath mila kar khaaey.
2490,hamara qiyam Madina mein tha aur ham par qahat ka daur-daurah hua. Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) hamein khajoor khaney ke liye detey they aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) guzartey huey ye keh kar jaya kartey they ke 2-2 khajoor aik sath mila kar na khana kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne doosrey sathi ki ijazat ke baghair aisa karne se mana farmaya hai.
2491,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs mushtarak ( saajhey (ke ghulam mein apna hissey aazad kar de aur uske paas sarey ghulam ki qeemat ke muwafiq maal ho to wo pura aazad ho jaeyga agar itna maal na ho to bas jitna hissey uska tha utnaa hi aazad hua. Ayub ne kaha ke ye mujhey malum nahi ke riwayat ka ye aakhiri hissey ''ghulam ka wahi hissey aazad hoga jo usney aazad kya hai'' ye Naafe ka apna qaul hai ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis mein dakhil hai.
2492,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs mushtarak ghulam mein se apna hissey aazad kar de to uske liye zaroori hai ke apne maal se ghulam ko poori aazadi dila de. lekin agar uske paas itna maal nahi hai to insaf ke sath ghulam ki qeemat lagai jaey. phir ghulam se kaha jaey ke (apni aazadi ki) koshish mein wo baqi hisse ki qeemat khud kamaa kar ada kar ley. lekin ghulam par uske liye koi dabaaw na daala jaey.
2493,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah ki hudood par qaaim rehney waley aur is mein ghus janey waley (yani khilaf karne waale) ki misal aisey logon ki si hai jinhoney aik kashtii ke silsiley mein Qura dala. jiske nateeje mein kuchh logon ko kashtii ke uper ka hissa aur kuchh ko nichey kaa. isliye jo log nichey waley they, unhein (dariya se) pani leney ke liye uper walon ke paas se guzarna padtaa. unhon-ne sochaa ke kyon na ham apne hi hisse mein aik suraakh kar lein taake uper walon ko ham koi takleef na dein. ab agar uper waley bhi nichey walon ko man-maanii karne dengey to kashtii waley tamam halaak ho jaeinge aur agar uper waley nichey walon ka hath pakad lein to ye khud bhi bachengey aur saari kashtii bhi bach jaeygi."
2494,"unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ( sura Nisa mein) us aayat ke barey mein puchha ( وإن خفتم‏ ( se ( ورباع‏ ( ''agar tum ko yatimon mein insaf na karne ka dar ho to jo auratein pasand aaein do-do, teen-teen, chaar-chaar nikah mein laao'' unhon-ne kaha mere bhaanjey ye aayat us yateem ladki ke barey mein hai jo apne wali (muhaafiz rishtedar jaisey chacheraa bhaaii, phoophii-zaad ya maamun-zaad bhaaii) ki parwarish mein ho aur tarkey ke maal mein uski saajhii ho aur wo uski maaldaarii aur khoobsoortii par farefta ho kar us se nikah kar lena chahey lekin pura mehar insaf se jitna usko aur jagah milta wo na de, to usey us se mana kar diya gaya ke aisi yateem ladkiyon se nikah kare. albatta agar unke sath unke wali insaf kar sakein aur unki haisiyat ke hisab se behtar se behtar tarze-amal mehar ke barey mein ikhtiyar karein (to is sura mein nikah karne ki ijazat hai) aur unse ye bhi keh diya gaya ke unke siwa jo bhi aurat unhein pasand ho unse wo nikah kar saktey hain. Urwa-bin-Zubair ne kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne batlaayaa, phir logon ne us aayat ke nazil honey ke baad) aisi ladkiyon se nikah ki ijazat ke barey mein) masla puchha to Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) ويستفتونك في Nisa ( ''aur aap se aurton ke barey mein ye log sawal kartey hain''. aagey farmaya aur tum unse nikah karna chahtey ho. ye jo is aayat mein hai aur jo Quran main tum par padha jata hai us se murad pehli aayat hai yani ''agar tum ko yatimon mein insaf na ho sakney ka dar ho to dusri auratein jo bhalii lagein unse nikah kar lo''. Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ye jo Allah ne dusri aayat mein farmaya aur tum unse nikah karna chahtey ho us se ye gharaz hai ke jo yateem ladki tumhari parwarish mein ho aur maal aur jamaal kam rakhti ho us se to tum nafrat kartey ho, isliye jis yateem ladki ke maal aur jamaal main tum ko raghbat ho us se bhi nikah na karo magar is sura mein jab insaf ke sath unka pura mehar ada karo."
2495,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Shufaa ka haq aisey maalon (zameen, jaaidaad wghaira) mein diya tha jinki taqseem na hui ho. lekin jab uski had bandi ho jaey aur rastey bhi badal diye jayen to phir Shufaa ka koi haq baqi nahi rahega."
2496,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har us jaaidaad mein Shufaa ka haq diya tha jiski shurakaa mein abhi taqseem na hui ho. lekin agar had bandi ho jaey aur rastey alag ho jayen to phir Shufaa ka haq baqi nahi rahtaa.
2497,maine Abul-Minhaal se Sauda sirf naqd ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke maine aur mere aik Sharik ne koi cheez (soney aur chandi ki) kharidi naqd par bhi aur udhaar par bhii. phir hamarey yahan Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) aaey to ham ne unse uske barey mein poochha. unhon-ne kaha ke maine aur mere Sharik Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi ye Sauda kiya tha aur ham ne iske mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke jo naqd ho wo ley lo aur jo udhaar ho usey chhod do.
2498,maine Abul-Minhaal se Sauda sirf naqd ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke maine aur mere aik Sharik ne koi cheez (soney aur chandi ki) kharidi naqd par bhi aur udhaar par bhii. phir hamarey yahan Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) aaey to ham ne unse iske barey mein poochha. unhon-ne kaha ke maine aur mere Sharik Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi ye Sauda kiya tha aur ham ne iske mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke jo naqd ho wo ley lo aur jo udhaar ho usey chhod do.
2499,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki zameen yahudiyon ko us shart par de di thi ke wo usmein mehnat karein aur boiin jotein . paidawar ka aadha hissey unhein mila karega .
2500,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bakriyan di thin ke qurbani ke liye unko sahaba mein taqseem kar din. phir aik saal ka bakri ka bachcha bach gaya to unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aqba se farmaya to uski qurbani kar ley.
2501,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko paya tha. unki walida Zainab-binte-Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aapko lekar hazir huin aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! us se bait ley lijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to abhi bachcha hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sar par hath phera aur unke liye dua ki aur Zohra-bin-Ma'bad se riwayat hai ke unke dada Abdullah-bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) unhein apne sath bazar ley jatey. wahan wo ghalla khareedtey. phir Abdullah-bin-Umar aur Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) unse miltey to wo kehtey ke hamein bhi us anaaj mein Sharik kar lo. kyonke aap ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne barkat ki dua ki hai. chunanche Abdullah-bin Hisham unhein bhi Sharik kar letey aur kabhi pura aik oont (ghalle ke saath) nafe mein paida kar letey aur usko ghar bhej detey.
2502,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko paya tha. unki walida Zainab-binte-Humaid (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aapko lekar hazir huin aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! us se bait ley lijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to abhi bachcha hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sar par hath phera aur unke liye dua ki aur Zohra-bin-Ma'bad se riwayat hai ke unke dada Abdullah-bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) unhein apne sath bazar ley jatey. wahan wo ghalla khareedtey. phir Abdullah-bin-Umar aur Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) unse miltey to wo kehtey ke hamein bhi us anaaj mein Sharik kar lo. kyonke aap ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne barkat ki dua ki hai. chunanche Abdullah-bin Hisham unhein bhi Sharik kar letey aur kabhi pura aik oont (ghalle ke saath) nafe mein paida kar letey aur usko ghar bhej detey.
2503,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne kisi saajhey ke ghulam ka apna hissey aazad kar diya to uske liye zaroori hai ke agar ghulam ki insaf ke muwafiq qeemat ke barabar uske paas maal ho to wo Sara ghulam aazad kara de. is tarah doosrey saajhiyon ko unke hissey ki qeemat ada kar di jaey aur us aazad kiye huey ghulam ka peechhaa chhod diya jaey.
2504,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne kisi (saajhey ke) ghulam ka apna hissey aazad kar diya to agar uske paas maal hai to pura ghulam aazad ho jaeyga warna baqi hisson ko aazad karaaney ke liye us se mehnat mazdoorii karaai jaey. lekin is silsiley main is par koi dabaaw na daala jaey.
2505,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chothi Zil-Hijja ki subah ko Haj ka talbiya kehtey huey jiske sath koi aur cheez (Umra) na milaate huey (Makka mein) dakhil huey. jab ham Makka pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se ham ne apne Haj ko Umra kar dala. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya ke (Umra ke arkaan ada karne ke baad Haj ke ehram tak) hamari beeviyan hamarey liye halal rahengii. is par logon mein charcha honey laga. Ata ne bayan kya ke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke kuchh log kehney lagey kya ham mein se koi Mina is tarah jaey ke mani uske zakar (private part) se tapak rahi ho. Jaabir ne hath se ishara bhi kya. ye baat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba dene khadey huey aur farmaya mujhey malum hua hai ke kuchh log is tarah ki baatein kar rahe hain. Allah ki qism mein un logon se zyada nek aur Allah se darney wala hun. agar mujhey wo baat pahley hi malum hoti jo ab malum hui hai to main qurbani ke janwar apne sath na laataa aur agar mere sath qurbani ke janwar na hotey to main bhi ehram khol detaa. is par Suraaqa-bin-Maalik-bin-Ja'sham khadey huey aur kaha ya Rasulullah! kya ye hukm (Haj ke dinon mein Umra) khas hamarey hi liye hai ya hamesha ke liye? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi balke hamesha ke liye hai. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) (Yaman se) aaey. ab ata aur Taaus mein se aik to yun kehta hai Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ehram ke waqt yun kaha thaa. لبيك بما أهل به رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم‏ aur doosra yun kehta hai ke unhon-ne لبيك بحجة رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم kahaa tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke wo apne ehram par qaaim rahen (jaisaa bhi unhon-ne baandha hai) aur unhein apni qurbani mein Sharik kar liya.
2506,nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chothi Zil-Hijja ki subah ko Haj ka talbiya kehtey huey jiske sath koi aur cheez (Umra) na milaate huey (Makka mein) dakhil huey. jab ham Makka pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se ham ne apne Haj ko Umra kar dala. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya ke (Umra ke arkaan ada karne ke baad Haj ke ehram tak) hamari beeviyan hamarey liye halal rahengii. is par logon mein charcha honey laga. Ata ne bayan kya ke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke kuchh log kehney lagey kya ham mein se koi Mina is tarah jaey ke mani uske zakar (private part) se tapak rahi ho. Jaabir ne hath se ishara bhi kya. ye baat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba dene khadey huey aur farmaya mujhey malum hua hai ke kuchh log is tarah ki baatein kar rahe hain. Allah ki qism mein un logon se zyada nek aur Allah se darney wala hun. agar mujhey wo baat pahley hi malum hoti jo ab malum hui hai to main qurbani ke janwar apne sath na laataa aur agar mere sath qurbani ke janwar na hotey to main bhi ehram khol detaa. is par Suraaqa-bin-Maalik-bin-Ja'sham khadey huey aur kaha ya Rasulullah! kya ye hukm (Haj ke dinon mein Umra) khas hamarey hi liye hai ya hamesha ke liye? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi balke hamesha ke liye hai. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) (Yaman se) aaey. ab ata aur Taaus mein se aik to yun kehta hai Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ehram ke waqt yun kaha thaa. لبيك بما أهل به رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم‏ aur doosra yun kehta hai ke unhon-ne لبيك بحجة رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم kahaa tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke wo apne ehram par qaaim rahen (jaisaa bhi unhon-ne baandha hai) aur unhein apni qurbani mein Sharik kar liyaa.
2507,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tahaama ke maqam zul-Hulaifa mein they ( ghaneemat mein) hamein bakriyan aur oont miley they. kuchh logon ne jaldi ki aur (jaanwar zabah karke) gosht ko haandiyon mein chadhaa diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se gosht ki haandiyon ko ulat diya gaya. phir (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne taqseem mein) das bakriyon ka aik oont ke barabar hissey rakha. aik oont bhag khada hua. qaum ke paas ghodon ki kami thi. aik shakhs ne oont ko teer mar kar rok liya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un janwaron mein bhi jangi janwaron ki tarah wahshat hoti hai. isliye jab tak unko na pakad sako to tum unke sath hi aisa sulook kya karo. Abaaya ne bayan kya ke mere dada ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah! hamein ummeed hai ya khatrah hai ke kahin kal dushman se mudbhed na ho jaey aur chhuri hamarey sath nahi hai. kya dhaar-daar lakdi se ham zabah kar saktey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, lekin zabah karne mein jaldi karo. jo cheez khoon baha de (usi se kaat daalo) agar is par Allah ka naam liya jaey to usko khaao aur naakhun aur daant se zabah na karo. uski wjah mein batlaataa hon daant to haddi hai aur naakhun habshiyon ki chhuriyaan hain."
